To build:

1. Make install lwes code. It will install by default into /usr/local. Make
sure you note the version and change the commands below to match.

2. Build the swig wrapper and library

swig -I/usr/local/include/lwes-0/lwes-0.22.2 -ruby lwes.i

ruby extconf.rb \
 --with-lwes-include=/usr/local/include/lwes-0/lwes-0.22.2 \
 --with-lwes-lib=/usr/local/lib

make

For examples on how to use lwes_functions.rb, look in the testing directory.
